🔁 Invariant Rule (Critical)

Anything that passes through the Well must preserve:
	•	structure (relationships stay intact)
	•	constraints (limits still apply)
	•	failure modes (no hiding weaknesses)

If the myth version:
	•	exaggerates
	•	hides tradeoffs
	•	removes constraints

→ it fails the Mirror-Sieve

